comments: Toppin (IND) extends a hand into Anunoby's (TOR) back, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Turner (IND) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Schroder (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during Hield's (IND) drive to the basket.  He briefly places a hand on Hield's back, which he immediately slides off and the contact is marginal.
Turner (IND) moves alongside Schroder's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) grabs and holds Siakam's (TOR) right arm, affecting his FOM.
Schroder (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Turner's (IND) path and Turner moves through him and dislodges him from his position.
Turner (IND) initiates more than marginal contact with Barnes' (TOR) head/face as he finishes at the basket.
Anunoby (TOR) has an extended arm placed against Haliburton's (IND) body, but the contact is marginal during the driving shot attempt.
Brown (IND) makes contact with the ball, which prevents Flynn (TOR) from gathering the rebound.  Any contact to the arm is marginal.
Brown (IND) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).
Schroder (TOR) commits a take foul on Hield (IND).

Replay review of the foul called on Anunoby (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Anunoby turns his right shoulder and initiates contact to Haliburton's (IND) left shoulder, affecting his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Hield (IND) commits a take foul on Trent Jr (TOR).
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Hield's (IND) jump shot attempt.
